57.1	The_Adventures_of_Tom_Sawyer	The Adventures of Tom Sawyer	The Adventures of Tom Sawyer by Mark Twain is an 1876 novel about a young boy growing up along the Mississippi River. The story is set in the Town of "St. Petersburg", inspired by Hannibal, Missouri, where Mark Twain lived.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg/220px-Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg
